{"id":80,"parent_id":73,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":80,"title":"John 7","subtitle":"","short_title":"John","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 7"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus’ kinsmen do not believe—He teaches His Father’s doctrine and proclaims His divine sonship—Truth may be known through obedience—Jesus offers living water to all people—The people have various opinions concerning Him."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.1","order":"03.06.007.9925"},["b","1"],"After these things Jesus walked in Galilee: for he would not walk in Jewry, because the Jews",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"sought"],"to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"kill"],"him."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.2","order":"03.06.007.9926"},["b","2"],"Now the Jews’",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"feast of tabernacles"],"was at hand."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.3","order":"03.06.007.9927"},["b","3"],"His",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"brethren"],"therefore said unto him, Depart hence, and go into Judæa, that thy disciples also may see the works that thou doest."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.4","order":"03.06.007.9928"},["b","4"],"For",["i","there is"],"no man",["i","that"],"doeth any thing in secret, and he himself seeketh to be known openly. If thou do these things, shew thyself to the world."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.5","order":"03.06.007.9929"},["b","5"],"For neither did his brethren believe in him."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.6","order":"03.06.007.9930"},["b","6"],"Then Jesus said unto them, My",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"time"],"is not yet come: but your time is alway ready."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.7","order":"03.06.007.9931"},["b","7"],"The world cannot hate you; but me it",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"hateth"],", because I testify of it, that the works thereof are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"evil"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.8","order":"03.06.007.9932"},["b","8"],"Go ye up unto this feast: I go not up yet unto this feast; for my time is not yet full come."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.9","order":"03.06.007.9933"},["b","9"],"When he had said these words unto them, he abode",["i","still"],"in Galilee."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.10","order":"03.06.007.9934"},["b","10"],"¶But when his brethren were gone up, then went he also up unto the feast, not openly, but as it were in secret."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.11","order":"03.06.007.9935"},["b","11"],"Then the Jews sought him at the feast, and said, Where is he?"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.12","order":"03.06.007.9936"},["b","12"],"And there was much murmuring among the people concerning him: for some said, He is a good man: others said, Nay; but he deceiveth the people."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.13","order":"03.06.007.9937"},["b","13"],"Howbeit no man spake openly of him for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"fear"],"of the Jews."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.14","order":"03.06.007.9938"},["b","14"],"¶Now about the midst of the feast Jesus went up into the temple, and taught."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.15","order":"03.06.007.9939"},["b","15"],"And the Jews",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"marvelled"],", saying, How knoweth this man letters, having never learned?"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.16","order":"03.06.007.9940"},["b","16"],"Jesus answered them, and said, My",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"doctrine"],"is not mine, but his that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"sent"],"me."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.17","order":"03.06.007.9941"},["b","17"],"If any man will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"do"],"his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"will"],", he shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"know"],"of the doctrine, whether it be of God, or",["i","whether"],"I speak of myself."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.18","order":"03.06.007.9942"},["b","18"],"He that speaketh of himself seeketh his own",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"glory"],": but he that seeketh his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"glory"],"that sent him, the same is true, and no unrighteousness is in him."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.19","order":"03.06.007.9943"},["b","19"],"Did not Moses give you the law, and",["i","yet"],"none of you keepeth the law? Why go ye about to kill me?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.20","order":"03.06.007.9944"},["b","20"],"The people answered and said, Thou hast a devil: who goeth about to kill thee?"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.21","order":"03.06.007.9945"},["b","21"],"Jesus answered and said unto them, I have done one work, and ye all marvel."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.22","order":"03.06.007.9946"},["b","22"],"Moses therefore gave unto you",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"circumcision"],"; (not because it is of Moses, but of the fathers;) and ye on the sabbath day circumcise a man."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.23","order":"03.06.007.9947"},["b","23"],"If a man on the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"sabbath"],"day receive circumcision, that the law of Moses should not be broken; are ye angry at me, because I have made a man every whit",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"whole"],"on the sabbath day?"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.24","order":"03.06.007.9948"},["b","24"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"Judge not"],"according to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"the"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_24c"},"appearance"],", but judge righteous judgment."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.25","order":"03.06.007.9949"},["b","25"],"Then said some of them of Jerusalem, Is not this he, whom they seek to kill?"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.26","order":"03.06.007.9950"},["b","26"],"But, lo, he speaketh boldly, and they say nothing unto him. Do the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"rulers"],"know indeed that this is the very Christ?"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.27","order":"03.06.007.9951"},["b","27"],"Howbeit we know this man whence he is: but when Christ cometh, no man knoweth whence he is."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.28","order":"03.06.007.9952"},["b","28"],"Then cried Jesus in the temple as he taught, saying, Ye both know me, and ye know whence I am: and I am not come of myself, but he that sent me is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"true"],", whom ye know not."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.29","order":"03.06.007.9953"},["b","29"],"But I know him: for I am from him, and he hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"sent"],"me."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.30","order":"03.06.007.9954"},["b","30"],"Then they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"sought"],"to take him: but no man laid hands on him, because his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_30b"},"hour"],"was not yet come."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.31","order":"03.06.007.9955"},["b","31"],"And many of the people believed on him, and said, When Christ cometh, will he do more miracles than these which this",["i","man"],"hath done?"],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.32","order":"03.06.007.9956"},["b","32"],"¶The Pharisees heard that the people murmured such things concerning him; and the Pharisees and the chief priests sent officers to take him."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.33","order":"03.06.007.9957"},["b","33"],"Then said Jesus unto them, Yet a little while am I with you, and",["i","then"],"I go unto him that sent me."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.34","order":"03.06.007.9958"},["b","34"],"Ye shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"seek"],"me, and shall not find",["i","me:"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_34b"},"where"],"I am,",["i",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_34c"},"thither"]],"ye",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_34d"},"cannot"],"come."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.35","order":"03.06.007.9959"},["b","35"],"Then said the Jews among themselves, Whither will he go, that we shall not find him? will he go unto the dispersed among the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"Gentiles"],", and teach the Gentiles?"],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.36","order":"03.06.007.9960"},["b","36"],"What",["i","manner of"],"saying is this that he said, Ye shall seek me, and shall not find",["i","me:"],"and where I am,",["i","thither"],"ye cannot come?"],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.37","order":"03.06.007.9961"},["b","37"],"In the last day, that great",["i","day"],"of the feast, Jesus stood and cried, saying, If any man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"thirst"],", let him come unto me, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_37b"},"drink"],"."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.38","order":"03.06.007.9962"},["b","38"],"He that believeth on me, as the scripture hath said, out of his belly shall flow rivers of living water."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.39","order":"03.06.007.9963"},["b","39"],"(But this spake he of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_39a"},"Spirit"],", which they that believe on him should receive:",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_39b"},"for"],"the Holy Ghost was not yet",["i","given;"],"because that Jesus was not yet glorified.)"],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.40","order":"03.06.007.9964"},["b","40"],"¶Many of the people therefore, when they heard this saying, said, Of a truth this is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_40a"},"Prophet"],"."],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.41","order":"03.06.007.9965"},["b","41"],"Others said, This is the Christ. But some said, Shall Christ come out of Galilee?"],["div",{"id":"42","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.42","order":"03.06.007.9966"},["b","42"],"Hath not the scripture said, That",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_42a"},"Christ"],"cometh of the seed of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_42b"},"David"],", and out of the town of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_42c"},"Bethlehem"],", where David was?"],["div",{"id":"43","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.43","order":"03.06.007.9967"},["b","43"],"So there was a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_43a"},"division"],"among the people because of him."],["div",{"id":"44","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.44","order":"03.06.007.9968"},["b","44"],"And some of them would have taken him; but no man laid hands on him."],["div",{"id":"45","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.45","order":"03.06.007.9969"},["b","45"],"¶Then came the officers to the chief priests and Pharisees; and they said unto them, Why have ye not brought him?"],["div",{"id":"46","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.46","order":"03.06.007.9970"},["b","46"],"The officers answered, Never man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_46a"},"spake"],"like this man."],["div",{"id":"47","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.47","order":"03.06.007.9971"},["b","47"],"Then answered them the Pharisees, Are ye also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_47a"},"deceived"],"?"],["div",{"id":"48","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.48","order":"03.06.007.9972"},["b","48"],"Have any of the rulers or of the Pharisees believed on him?"],["div",{"id":"49","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.49","order":"03.06.007.9973"},["b","49"],"But this people who knoweth not the law are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_49a"},"cursed"],"."],["div",{"id":"50","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.50","order":"03.06.007.9974"},["b","50"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_50a"},"Nicodemus"],"saith unto them, (he that came to Jesus by night, being one of them,)"],["div",{"id":"51","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.51","order":"03.06.007.9975"},["b","51"],"Doth our law judge",["i","any"],"man, before it hear him, and know what he doeth?"],["div",{"id":"52","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.52","order":"03.06.007.9976"},["b","52"],"They answered and said unto him, Art thou also of Galilee? Search, and look: for out of Galilee ariseth no prophet."],["div",{"id":"53","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.53","order":"03.06.007.9977"},["b","53"],"And every man went unto his own house."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.1a","order":"03.06.007.9978"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/5.16.16,18"},"John 5:16 (16, 18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.1b","order":"03.06.007.9980"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/11.53.53-54"},"John 11:53 (53–54)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.2a","order":"03.06.007.9982"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/23.34.34-43"},"Lev. 23:34 (34–43)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.3a","order":"03.06.007.9984"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/12.46"},"Matt. 12:46"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.5"},"1 Cor. 9:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.6a","order":"03.06.007.9986"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/26.18"},"Matt. 26:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.7a","order":"03.06.007.9988"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/16.2.1-3"},"1 Ne. 16:2 (1–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.7b","order":"03.06.007.9990"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/evil"},"TG Evil"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.13a","order":"03.06.007.9992"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/19.38"},"John 19:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.15a","order":"03.06.007.9994"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/2.46.46-47"},"Luke 2:46 (46–47)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.16a","order":"03.06.007.9996"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/7.28"},"Matt. 7:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/8.28"},"John 8:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.21"},"2 Ne. 31:21"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gospel"},"TG Gospel"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-teaching-mode-of"},"Jesus Christ, Teaching Mode of"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.16b","order":"03.06.007.9998"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-authority-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Authority of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-messenger-of-the-covenant"},"Jesus Christ, Messenger of the Covenant"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.17a","order":"03.06.007.10000"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/good-works"},"TG Good Works"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/obedience"},"Obedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.17b","order":"03.06.007.10002"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-will-of"},"TG God, Will of"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.17c","order":"03.06.007.10004"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/discernment-spiritual"},"TG Discernment, Spiritual"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/testimony"},"Testimony"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/truth"},"Truth"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.18a","order":"03.06.007.10006"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/5.41.41-43"},"John 5:41 (41–43)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.18b","order":"03.06.007.10008"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/8.50"},"John 8:50"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.67"},"D&C 88:67"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/4